Class XMLLazyResultSet

java.lang.Object
ca.phon.query.db.xml.XMLResultSet
ca.phon.query.db.xml.XMLLazyResultSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
ResultSet, JAXBWrapper<ResultSetType>, java.lang.Iterable<Result>
public class XMLLazyResultSet
extends XMLResultSet
Similar to XMLResultSet, except loading of result set data is lazy (i.e., delayed as long as possible).
